    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Seeds produced by the species Cicer arietinum. These yellow brown seeds are borne one or two to a pod and are an important food staple in India, Africa, and Central and South America.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
